\v 2 Abraham was the father of Isaac, Isaac the father of Yacob (Grk: Yakob), Yacob the father of YudahВҰ22 (Grk: YoudasВҰ22) and hisВҰ26 brothersВҰ25.
\v 3 YudahВҰ27 was the father of Perez (Grk: FaresВҰ31) and Zerah (Grk: ZaraВҰ34) through Tamar (Grk: ThamarВҰ37), Perez the father of Hezron (Grk: Hezrom), Hezron the father of AramВҰ47,
\v 4 AramВҰ48 the father of Aminadab, Aminadab the father of Nahshon (Grk: NaassonВҰ57), Nahshon the father of SalmonВҰ62,
\v 5 SalmonВҰ63 the father of Boaz (Grk: Boes) through RahabВҰ70, Boaz the father of Obed (Grk: Yobed) through RuthВҰ78 (Grk: Routh), and Obed the father of Jesse (Grk: YessaiВҰ83),
\v 6 andВҰ85 Jesse the father of DavidВҰ88 the kingВҰ90.
\p David was the father of SolomonВҰ97 (Grk: Solomona) through Uriah's (Grk: OuriasВҰ101) wifeВҰ99,
\v 7 SolomonВҰ102 was the father of Rehoboam (Grk: Roboam), Rehoboam the father of Abiyah (Grk: Abia), Abiyah the father of Asa (Grk: Asaf),
\v 8 Asa the father of Jehoshapat (Grk: Yosafat). Jehoshapat the father of Joram (Grk: YoramВҰ126), Joram the father of UzziahВҰ131 (Grk: OziasВҰ131),
\v 9 UzziahВҰ132 the father of Jotham (Grk: YoathamВҰ136), Jotham the father of Ahaz (Grk: AchazВҰ141), Ahaz the father of HezekiahВҰ146 (Grk: Hezekias),
\v 10 HezekiahВҰ147 the father of Manasseh (Grk: Manasse), Manasseh the father of Amon (Grk: AmosВҰ157), Amon the father of Josiah (Grk: Yosias),
\v 11 \x + \xo 1:11: \xt 2Ki 24:14-15; 2Ch 36:10; Jer 27:20.\x*Josiah was the father of Jechoniah (Grk: YechoniasВҰ169) and hisВҰ173 brothersВҰ172, when they were deportedВҰ176 to Babylon (Grk: BabulonosВҰ177).
\p
\v 12 And afterВҰ178 the deportationВҰ181 to BabylonВҰ182, Jechoniah was the father of Shealtiel (Grk: SalathielВҰ187), Shealtiel was the father of Zerubbabel (Grk: ZorobabelВҰ193),
\v 13 Zerubbabel was the father of Abiud (Grk: AbioudВҰ199), Abiud was the father of Eliakim, and Eliakim the father of AzorВҰ209,
\v 14 AzorВҰ210 the father of Zadok, Zadok the father of Achim, Achim the father of EliudВҰ224 (Grk: ElioudВҰ224),
\v 15 EliudВҰ225 the father of Eleazar, Eleazar the father of Matthan, Matthan the father of YacobВҰ239 (Grk: Yakob),
\v 16 YacobВҰ240 the father of Yosef, the husbandВҰ246 of Maria (Grk: Marias) who \nd Yeshua\nd* (Grk: Yaysous), the one calledВҰ253 the \nd messiahВҰ254\nd* was born to.
\p
\v 17 SoВҰ256 the generations from AbrahamВҰ260 to David numbered fourteen, from David to the deportation to Babylon there were fourteen generations, and from the deportation to Babylon to the \nd messiahВҰ281\nd* there were fourteen generations.
\s1 The birth of the messiah
