\r (Luke 1:26-38; 2:1-7)
\p
\v 18 \x + \xo 1:18: \xt Luk 1:27.\x*Now this is how the birthВҰ290 of \nd Yeshua\nd* came about: MariaВҰ299 hisВҰ298 motherВҰ297 was engaged to Yosef. ButВҰ285 beforeВҰ302 they came togetherВҰ304, sheВҰ306 was foundВҰ306 to be pregnant through \add the work of\add* the holy \nd spiritВҰ311\nd*.
