\v 20 But as he was pondering this, one of Yahweh's messengersВҰ335 appearedВҰ340 to him in a dreamВҰ339 and told him, вҖңYosef, descendant of \add King\add* DavidВҰ345, don'tВҰ346 be afraidВҰ347 to marry MariaВҰ349, becauseВҰ354 the baby in her has been conceived by the holy \nd spiritВҰ359\nd*.
\v 21 \x + \xo 1:21: \xt Luk 1:31.\x*In due course she'll have a son andВҰ364 you'll nameВҰ369 him \nd Yeshua\nd*, becauseВҰ373 he'll save hisВҰ370 peopleВҰ376 from theirВҰ381 sinsВҰ380.вҖқ
\p
\v 22 Now all this happened in fulfilmentВҰ387 of what \nd YahwehВҰ392\nd* had said throughВҰ393 the prophetВҰ396,
