\p
\v 24 ThenВҰ423 Yosef got up and did what Yahweh's messengerВҰ434 had commandedВҰ431 him, and he went ahead and married Maria,
\v 25 \x + \xo 1:25: \xt Luk 2:21.\x*but he didn'tВҰ443 sleep with her untilВҰ447 after she gave birth. And Yosef named the boy \nd Yeshua\nd*.
