\v 9 SoВҰ617 when the kingВҰ621 had finished speaking, they departed, and the starВҰ626 which they could seeВҰ624 in the east went ahead of them and stopped above the place whereВҰ640 the childВҰ644 was.
\v 10 Seeing this, the watchers of signs were very happy indeed.
