\v 13 After they'd departed, one of \nd Yahweh's\nd* messengersВҰ714 appearedВҰ716 to Yosef in a dreamВҰ718 and said, вҖңGet up and take the child and hisВҰ735 motherВҰ734 and flee to EgyptВҰ739 \add (Mitsrayim)\add*. Remain thereВҰ742 untilВҰ743 I tell you, becauseВҰ749 \add King\add* HerodВҰ750 will soon search for the child in order to killВҰ757 him.вҖқ
