\v 15 вҖң\wj Just allowВҰ1282 it,\wj*вҖқ answeredВҰ1262 \nd Yeshua\nd*, вҖң\wj becauseВҰ1273 we need to do what righteousnessВҰ1280 requires.\wj*вҖқ So Yohan immersed him.
