\v 17 \x + \xo 3:17: \xt Gen 22:2; Psa 2:7; Isa 42:1; Mat 12:18; 17:5; Mrk 1:11; Luk 9:35.\x*ThenВҰ1321, wowВҰ1322, a voiceВҰ1323 came from the sky and said, вҖңThis is myВҰ1338 son that I love and I'm pleasedВҰ1343 with.вҖқ
