\p
\v 7 \x + \xo 4:7: \xt Deu 6:16.\x*вҖң\wj But it's also writtenВҰ1478,\wj*вҖқ \nd Yeshua\nd* answered, вҖң\wj that youВҰ1485 shouldn'tВҰ1479 test \+nd YahwehВҰ1482\+nd* yourВҰ1485 \+nd GodВҰ1484\+nd*.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 8 Then the devilВҰ1490 took him to a very highВҰ1493 mountainВҰ1492 and showed him all the countries of the worldВҰ1504 with all theirВҰ1508 splendour,
\v 9 then told himВҰ1512, вҖңI'll give all of theseВҰ1513 to you if you get down \add вүҲon your face\add* in front of me.вҖқ
\p
\v 10 \x + \xo 4:10: \xt Deu 6:13.\x*вҖң\wj Go away, SatanВҰ1531,\wj*вҖқ \nd Yeshua\nd* replied, вҖң\wj becauseВҰ1533 it's writtenВҰ1532 \+add in the scriptures\+add* that you should worship \+nd YahwehВҰ1534\+nd* yourВҰ1537 \+nd GodВҰ1536\+nd* and should only serve him.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 11 Then the devilВҰ1548 left him, and \add God's\add* messengersВҰ1551 came and looked after him.
