\v 13 \x + \xo 4:13: \xt Yhn 2:12.\x*He moved from \nd NazarethВҰ1572\nd* across to CapernaumВҰ1576 beside the lake in the regionВҰ1583 thatВҰ1577 had been given to the tribes of Zebulun andВҰ1585 Naftali,
