\p
\v 17 \x + \xo 4:17: \xt Mat 3:2.\x*From then onwards, \nd Yeshua\nd* started preachingВҰ1643 andВҰ1644 telling people to turn from their sins becauseВҰ1648 the heavenlyВҰ1652 kingdomВҰ1650 is close.
