\v 28 вҖң\nd MasterВҰ9811\nd*,вҖқ called PeterВҰ9808, вҖңif it's you, commandВҰ9816 me to comeВҰ9819 to you on the lake.вҖқ
\p
\v 29 вҖң\wj Come!\wj*вҖқ he saidВҰ9828. SoВҰ9827 PeterВҰ9836 climbed \add over the back\add* of the boatВҰ9834 andВҰ9827 started walking across the lake towards \nd Yeshua\nd*,
\v 30 butВҰ9849 when he looked \add around\add* at the windВҰ9851, he lost his nerve and started sinking and yelledВҰ9859 out, вҖң\nd MasterВҰ9861\nd*, saveВҰ9862 me!вҖқ
\v 31 Immediately \nd Yeshua\nd* stretchedВҰ9868 out hisВҰ9872 handВҰ9870 and tookВҰ9871 hold of Peter and said to him, вҖң\wj Your faithВҰ9877 is weak becauseВҰ9878 why did you doubtВҰ9880?\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 32 ThenВҰ9881 as soon as the two of them climbed into the boatВҰ9887, the windВҰ9890 diedВҰ9888 down
