\r (Mark 6:53-56)
\p
\v 34 SoВҰ9906 thenВҰ9906 theyВҰ9908 finished crossingВҰ9907 the lake andВҰ9906 got out at GennesaretВҰ9914.
\v 35 The people there recognisedВҰ9916 Yeshua andВҰ9915 sentВҰ9923 news to all the surroundingВҰ9927 regionВҰ9927. SoВҰ9915 the people broughtВҰ9930 all their sickВҰ9934 relatives to him
\v 36 and begged him even to just let them touchВҰ9941 the edge of hisВҰ9946 robe because everyone who did that was healed.
\c 15
\s1 Obeying God versus tradition
\rem /s1 The Tradition of the Elders; The Teaching of the Ancestors; Clean and Unclean; Jesus Teaches about Inner Purity
\r (Mark 7:1-13)
\p
\v 1 Then some from the Pharisees' partyВҰ9963 and teachersВҰ9966 of the law from Yerushalem arrived and asked \nd Yeshua\nd*,
\v 2 вҖңWhy do yourВҰ9973 followers breakВҰ9974 the traditionsВҰ9976 handed down by our eldersВҰ9978? They're not practicing the washingВҰ9981 handsВҰ9983 ceremony before eatingВҰ9987.вҖқ
\p
\v 3 вҖң\wj Well why also do you breakВҰ9998 God's commandВҰ10000 becauseВҰ10003 of yourВҰ10006 traditionВҰ10005?\wj*вҖқ Yeshua respondedВҰ9992.
\v 4 \x + \xo 15:4: a \xt Exo 20:12; Deu 5:16; \xo b \xt Exo 21:17; Lev 20:9.\x*вҖң\wj \+nd GodВҰ10009\+nd* told us to honourВҰ10013 our father and our mother, and also that anyone who speaksВҰ10023 evil about their father or mother deserves the deathВҰ10027 penalty.\wj*
\v 5 \wj But you all sayВҰ10036 that anyone who tells their fatherВҰ10038 or motherВҰ10041 that whatever \+add help\+add* they may have expected from you is now given as a giftВҰ10042,\wj*
\v 6 \wj thenВҰ10064 you say that they're not \+add actually\+add* dishonouring their parents. SoВҰ10064 by saying that, you're overriding God's messageВҰ10069 with yourВҰ10076 own traditionВҰ10075.\wj*
\v 7 \wj You hypocrites! The prophetВҰ10079 Yeshayah was rightВҰ10078 about youВҰ10081 all when he wrote:\wj*\x + \xo 15:7-9: \xt Isa 29:13 (LXX).\x*
\q1
\v 8 \wj вҖҳThese peopleВҰ10087 honourВҰ10096 me with their lipsВҰ10094,\wj*
\q2 \wj But their heartsВҰ10099 are far away from me.\wj*
\q1
\v 9 \wj Their worshipВҰ10109 of me is uselessВҰ10107,\wj*
\q2 \wj They teachВҰ10111 humanВҰ10114 ideas as if they're commandsВҰ10113.вҖҷ\wj* вҖқ
\s1 True вҖҳdirtinessвҖҷ
