\v 18 вҖң\wj ListenВҰ13703, we're goingВҰ13704 to YerushalemВҰ13706 and humanity's child will be handed over to the chiefВҰ13714 priestsВҰ13714 and the religiousВҰ13716 teachersВҰ13716, and theyВҰ13718 will condemnВҰ13718 himВҰ13719 to deathВҰ13722\wj*
\v 19 \wj and hand him over to the non-Jews to be mocked and flogged and executedВҰ13734 on a stakeВҰ13734, and then on the thirdВҰ13737 dayВҰ13738 he will come back to life.\wj*вҖқ
