\p вҖңPromise that myВҰ13778 twoВҰ13776 sonsВҰ13777 will be able to sitВҰ13773 beside you in the kingdomВҰ13790,вҖқ she saidВҰ13762, вҖңone on the rightВҰ13781 andВҰ13761 one on the left.вҖқ
\p
\v 22 But \nd Yeshua\nd* answeredВҰ13792, вҖң\wj You all don'tВҰ13798 realise what you're asking. Do you think you'll be able to bear the suffering thatВҰ13808 I will have to suffer?\wj*вҖқ
\p вҖңYes,вҖқ they replied, вҖңwe can.вҖқ
