\p
\v 34 \nd YeshuaВҰ14099\nd* felt compassionateВҰ14096 towards them and touchedВҰ14100 theirВҰ14105 eyesВҰ14104 \add with his fingers\add* and thenВҰ14097 straight away they were able to see, and they followedВҰ14114 afterВҰ14115 himВҰ14115.
