\p
\v 1 When theyВҰ14118 were getting close to Yerushalem andВҰ14121 arrived at BethphageВҰ14125 on the MtВҰ14129. of OlivesВҰ14131, \nd Yeshua\nd* sentВҰ14135 twoВҰ14136 of his apprenticesВҰ14137 ahead,
\v 2 telling them, вҖң\wj Go ahead to the next villageВҰ14144 and in frontВҰ14146 of you you'll see a donkey tied up and her colt near her. Untie the donkey and bringВҰ14159 them back here to me.\wj*
\v 3 \wj ButВҰ14162 if anyoneВҰ14165 says anythingВҰ14168 to you, just tell them that the \+nd masterВҰ14173\+nd* needs them, andВҰ14162 they'll let you take them.\wj*вҖқ
\p
