\p
\v 6 SoВҰ14224 the \add two\add* apprenticesВҰ14226 left andВҰ14227 did what \nd YeshuaВҰ14235\nd* had instructed them.
\v 7 They broughtВҰ14237 back the donkeyВҰ14239 and the colt, and they put theirВҰ14249 coatsВҰ14250 on them and he satВҰ14256 on them.
\v 8 ThenВҰ14262 the hugeВҰ14263 crowdВҰ14264 spread their coatsВҰ14269 on the road, while othersВҰ14273 cut branchesВҰ14276 off treesВҰ14279 andВҰ14262 spread them on the road.
\v 9 \x + \xo 21:9: \xt Psa 118:25-26.\x*The crowd that walked ahead of himВҰ14291 andВҰ14292 the crowd that followedВҰ14294 along behind all yelled out, вҖңDavid's descendant, honoured saviour! Blessed one who comes in \nd Yahweh's\nd* nameВҰ14306! Honoured saviour in the highestВҰ14311!вҖқ
\p
\v 10 As they entered Yerushalem, everyone in the cityВҰ14321 was stunned, asking, вҖңWho is this?вҖқ
\p
\v 11 The crowdsВҰ14329 responded, вҖңIt's the prophet \nd Yeshua\nd*вҖ”the prophet from \nd NazarethВҰ14340\nd* in the GalileeВҰ14342!вҖқ
