\v 12 ThenВҰ14343 \nd Yeshua\nd* \add dismounted and\add* entered the temple. He drove out those who were buyingВҰ14358 and selling in the temple, and overturnedВҰ14367 the tablesВҰ14364 of the moneychangersВҰ14366 and the seatsВҰ14370 of those who were selling dovesВҰ14374,
\v 13 \x + \xo 21:13: \xt Isa 56:7; Jer 7:11.\x*telling them, вҖң\wj It was writtenВҰ14378 that myВҰ14381 house will be calledВҰ14384 a house of prayerВҰ14383, but you all are makingВҰ14389 it a hideoutВҰ14390 of robbersВҰ14391.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 14 Those in the templeВҰ14403 who were blindВҰ14396 or lame approachedВҰ14393 Yeshua andВҰ14392 he healedВҰ14405 them.
