\p вҖң\wj Yes, I can,\wj*вҖқ \nd Yeshua\nd* respondedВҰ14434. вҖң\wj Didn't you ever read \+add where it says\+add* вҖҳYou caused praisesВҰ14456 to come from the lips of infantsВҰ14452 and babiesвҖҷ?\wj*вҖқ
