\v 23 When Yeshua went back into the templeВҰ14588 and started teachingВҰ14592 \add the peopleВҰ14599\add*, the chiefВҰ14594 priestsВҰ14594 and the Jewish eldersВҰ14597 came and challenged him, вҖңWhat authority do you have to do theseВҰ14604 things?вҖқ
\p
\v 24 вҖң\wj Well, I have one question for you first,\wj*вҖқ \nd Yeshua\nd* answered. вҖң\wj If you answer it, thenВҰ14615 I'll tell you all about my authorityВҰ14640 to do theseВҰ14641 things.\wj*
\v 25 \wj SoВҰ14656, whereВҰ14647 did Yohan's practice of immersionВҰ14644 come from?\wj*вҖқ
\p They discussed this amongВҰ14659 themselvesВҰ14660, saying, вҖңIf we say from heaven, he'll ask us why we didn'tВҰ14671 believeВҰ14672 Yohan.
\v 26 But if we sayВҰ14676 it was a humanВҰ14678 idea, then the crowdВҰ14682 might revolt against us becauseВҰ14684 they consider Yohan to be a prophetВҰ14686.вҖқ
