\v 31 \wj But as for the resurrectionВҰ15634 of the deadВҰ15636, isn'tВҰ15637 it \+add written in the scriptures\+add* that \+nd GodВҰ15644\+nd* said,\wj*
\v 32 \x + \xo 22:32: \xt Exo 3:6.\x*\wj вҖҳ\+em I am\+em* Abraham's god and Isaac's god and Yacob's god.вҖҷ? So \nd GodВҰ15649\nd* is not the god of the dead, but of the livingВҰ15666.\wj*вҖқ
\p
\v 33 When the crowdsВҰ15670 heardВҰ15668 his answer, theyВҰ15671 were amazedВҰ15671 at his teachingВҰ15674.
\s1 The most important command
