\v 39 \x + \xo 22:39: \xt Lev 19:18.\x*\wj The next is similarВҰ15748 to itВҰ15751: You should love yourВҰ15755 neighbourВҰ15754 like yourselfВҰ15757.\wj*
\v 40 \x + \xo 22:35-40: \xt Luk 10:25-28.\x*\wj Everything from the Torah andВҰ15767 \+add the writings of\+add* the prophetsВҰ15769 just follows on from those twoВҰ15761 commandsВҰ15762.\wj*вҖқ
\s1 The question about the messiah
