\v 54 The \add Roman\add* officer and his soldiers who were guardingВҰ20929 \nd Yeshua\nd* were very frightened when they felt the earthquakeВҰ20934 and saw what happened, and said, вҖңThis man really was a son of \nd GodВҰ20948\nd*!вҖқ
