\v 55 \x + \xo 27:55-56: \xt Luk 8:2-3.\x*There were many womenВҰ20956 watching all this from a distanceвҖ”they were those who from GalileeВҰ20967 who had followedВҰ20962 \nd Yeshua\nd* andВҰ20952 looked \nd afterВҰ20964\nd* himВҰ20970,
