\v 2 ThenВҰ21208, wowВҰ21209, there was a massive earthquakeВҰ21210 becauseВҰ21214 one of \nd Yahweh's\nd* messengersВҰ21213 had comeВҰ21216 down from heavenВҰ21220 and approachedВҰ21222 the tomb. He had rolledВҰ21223 away the stoneВҰ21225 and was now sittingВҰ21230 on itВҰ21232.
\v 3 He looked as if you were watching lightningВҰ21241 andВҰ21242 hisВҰ21239 clothesВҰ21244 were extremely whiteВҰ21246.
\v 4 The guardsВҰ21258 \add at the tomb\add* shook with fearВҰ21254 when they saw himВҰ21255 andВҰ21259 thenВҰ21251 they fainted.
\p
\v 5 ThenВҰ21266 the messengerВҰ21268 spoke to the womenВҰ21271, вҖңDon't be scared becauseВҰ21277 I know that both of you are lookingВҰ21282 forВҰ21282 \nd Yeshua\nd* who was executedВҰ21281 on a stakeВҰ21281.
\v 6 He isn'tВҰ21283 here, becauseВҰ21287 he came back to life just like he saidВҰ21289 he would. Go inside and seeВҰ21291 the placeВҰ21293 whereВҰ21294 his \add body\add* was lyingВҰ21295
\v 7 and thenВҰ21298 leave straight away and go and tell hisВҰ21304 followers that he has come alive again and will go ahead of you all to GalileeВҰ21316. You'll seeВҰ21311 him when you get thereВҰ21317. ListenВҰ21320, I've told you now.вҖқ
\p
\v 8 SoВҰ21323 theyВҰ21335 went off quicklyВҰ21326 with a mixture of fearВҰ21331 and incredible happiness, and ranВҰ21335 \add back\add* to tell Yeshua's followers.
\p
\v 9 ThenВҰ21347, wowВҰ21349, \nd Yeshua\nd* met them \add on the path\add* and greeted them. The two womenВҰ21357 went close \add and knelt down\add* and tookВҰ21360 hold of hisВҰ21361 feetВҰ21363 and lowered their heads.
\v 10 Then \nd Yeshua\nd* spoke again, вҖң\wj Don't be scared. Go now and tell myВҰ21379 brothersВҰ21378 so they'll goВҰ21382 up to GalileeВҰ21385 and then they'll see me thereВҰ21388.\wj*вҖқ
\s1 The guards are paid to lie
\rem /s1 The Report of the Guard; The Guards' Report
\p
\v 11 After they'd left, some of the guardsВҰ21398 \add from the tomb\add* went into the cityВҰ21402 andВҰ21393 told the chiefВҰ21406 priestsВҰ21406 everything that had happened,
\v 12 so they met togetherВҰ21412 with the eldersВҰ21415 andВҰ21411 after some discussion, they gaveВҰ21425 a generous amount to the soldiersВҰ21427
\v 13 and told them, вҖңTell everyone that his followers came in the dark and stoleВҰ21437 his body when you had fallen asleepВҰ21440.
\v 14 If the governorВҰ21449 hears about it, we'll butter him up so that youВҰ21454 won't need to be afraid \add of getting punished\add*.вҖқ
\p
\v 15 SoВҰ21459 they took the money andВҰ21459 did what they had been asked.
\s1 Yeshua commissions his apprentices as missionaries
